OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Ffor most this evening and staying dry.
OL,7,FA fine night to come with mostly clear
OL,8,Fskies across the region. Some cloud
OL,9,Fand hill fog possibly forming across
OL,10,Fhigh ground to the west. Winds
OL,11,Fremaining light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FBright and sunny for most,
OL,14,Fturning hot or very hot by the
OL,15,Fafternoon. The wind is expected to
OL,16,Fremain light, so won't give much
OL,17,Frespite from the heat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
