OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and sunny with hot afternoons.
OL,7,FChance of isolated thundery showers at
OL,8,Ffirst, mainly affecting hills.
OL,9,FFreshening north-easterly breeze by
OL,10,FSunday. Temperatures above average
OL,11,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
